    director {
      name: "Chris Columbus"
    }
    rating: "Very Good"
    comments: "Does a very good job at building the world and installing a lot of the elements from the books into the movies (also staying pretty true to the books); gets the most out of his actors and does a good job in getting the joy and innocence out of the child actors; brings his typical light-hearted tone that he has in his other movies"
  }
