    rating: "Very Good"
    comments: "Filled with many iconic lines that are instantly quotable (but is pretty safe overall given that it is a light-hearted children\'s movie), the symbolism is pretty similar to that of the books, the foreshadowing helps build the rest of the franchise and who the main antagonist will be for Harry to fight"
