  final_notes: "Some bias as this was one of my favorite movies growing up as a child"
  overall: "Overall, a great adaptation of one of the most iconic contemporary children\'s books as they build a world that has spawned one of the biggest franchises in film history, through its production design, costumes, score, and acting as we are transported outside the realm of reality to see kids try to find their part in the Wizarding World"
